DESCRIPTION:Join us on Wednesday\, July 1\, from 4-7 PM at Whispering Vine South Creek for a Belle Glos tasting featuring four California Pinot Noirs: Clark & Telephone\, Las Alturas\, Dairyman and Balade.\nTasting Fee: $35 per person (Buy a tasting bottle and your fee is refunded.)\nFeatured Wines:\n- Belle Glos Clark & Telephone Vineyard Pinot Noir 2024 - Santa Maria Valley Pinot Noir with cranberry\, raspberry jam\, cedar\, clove and a warm\, structured finish.\n- Belle Glos Las Alturas Vineyard Pinot Noir 2023 - Santa Lucia Highlands Pinot Noir with bing cherry\, dried fig\, cassis\, dark chocolate and mouthwatering acidity.\n- Belle Glos Dairyman Vineyard Pinot Noir 2024 - Russian River Valley Pinot Noir with dark chocolate\, black cherry\, blackberry pie\, cedar and refined tannins.\n- Belle Glos Balade Pinot Noir 2023 - Santa Rita Hills Pinot Noir with blackberry\, sage\, cherry\, dark chocolate\, boysenberry and a long finish.\nCome taste through Belle Glos and find your favorite bottle. Buy a tasting bottle and your fee is refunded.
LOCATION:85 Foothill Rd Ste 1 Reno\, NV 89511
SUMMARY:Belle Glos Tasting
END:VEVENT
END:VCALENDAR